<a href="/questions/1422374-did-anyone-else-discover-that-this-book-is">Did anyone else discover that this book is based on an actual crime? Right down to the nitty gritty details. I was surprised the author didn&#39;t acknowledge this because it had to be the inspiration for Diane&#39;s secret. If you&#39;re curious, do an online search on the Marie Robard case.</a>
