<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    &lt;spoiler&gt;Diane commits suicide and Kit is not implicated in any of the deaths. She continues working with Dr Severin and is very successful. Years lat<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    &lt;spoiler&gt;Diane commits suicide and Kit is not implicated in any of the deaths. She continues working with Dr Severin and is very successful. Years later, Diane's mother writes to Kit and includes a picture of her husband Steve. Kit realizes that Steve is the man she knew as a teenager who came on to her in his car. She told that story to Diane at camp, when Diane was living with her mom and then-boyfriend Steve. Diane tried to tell her mother but she didn't believe her, and Diane was sent to live with her dad. Kit realizes that telling her secret at camp was the real catalyst for everything that happened between her and Diane.&lt;/spoiler&gt;<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
