<span id="freeTextContainer5738866388646006662">I love a beautifully written thriller -- and this is exactly that. Not a who-done-it, but a why-done-it, with palpable dread on every page. And, as my own readers know, I love dread. And so I loved this exquisite novel.</span>

          </span>
